OL,3,CPedestrian in 70s in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after collision with double-
OL,5,Cdecker bus
OL,7,FA woman is in a life-threatening
OL,8,Fcondition in hospital after being
OL,9,Finvolved in a collision with a double-
OL,10,Fdecker bus in Aldershot.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,FHospital Hill, between the junctions
OL,14,Fof Badajos Road and Pennefather's
OL,15,FRoad, between 1.19pm and 1.30pm on
OL,16,FSaturday. (2 May)
OL,18,FThe pedestrian, a woman in her 70s
OL,19,Ffrom Aldershot ` was taken to hospital
OL,20,Fwith serious, potentially life-
OL,21,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
