OL,3,CPedestrian in 70s in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after collision with double-
OL,5,Cdecker bus
OL,7,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We would like to hear from anyone who
OL,9,Fwas in the area at the time of the
OL,10,Fcollision.
OL,12,F"Do you recall witnessing anything of
OL,13,Fthe incident? Do you have any dash cam
OL,14,Ffootage of collision?
OL,16,F"If you can help us with any of the
OL,17,Fabove, please call 101 and quote
OL,18,Fincident number 44260206132."
